<subSubSection id="C350656FAE32FFABFF753E1EFA6FD4B3" pageId="4" pageNumber="557" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BF536E4AE32FFABFF753E1EFA6FD4B3" blockId="4.[151,1437,1405,1612]" pageId="4" pageNumber="557">
<emphasis id="B93EEAF6AE32FFABFF753E1EFEF8D4FB" bold="true" box="[151,274,1405,1431]" pageId="4" pageNumber="557">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Antenna brownish yellow, except black scape. Pterostigma dark brown, short and wide, rectangular, posterior margin reaching R 
<subScript id="17CE34A1AE32FFABFE303ED7FE01D4AE" attach="left" box="[466,491,1460,1474]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="557">2+3</subScript>
. M 
<subScript id="17CE34A1AE32FFABFDF03ED7FDF0D4AE" attach="left" box="[530,538,1460,1474]" fontSize="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="557">2</subScript>
apically abbreviated, not reaching wing margin. Right surstylus about 2.0 times longer than wide, apically widely obtuse; left surstylus slightly widened with a distinct incision at apical margin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C350656FAE32FFABFF253E8AFDA4D768" box="[199,590,1513,1540]" pageId="4" pageNumber="557" type="distribution">
